# Network Traffic Protocol Fingerprinting (Task 28)

## 1. Project Overview
This project focuses on identifying network protocols (like DNS, HTTP, VoIP) using Machine Learning, specifically for securing aviation communication.

## 2. Dataset
- **Name:** ISCX VPN-nonVPN Dataset.
- **Source:** University of New Brunswick (UNB).

## 3. Technology Stack
- **Language:** Python.
- **Environment:** Google Colab / Jupyter Notebook.
- **Algorithms:** Random Forest / XGBoost.

## 4. Evaluation Metrics (Results)
- **Target Accuracy:** > 92%
- **Macro F1-score:** > 0.88
